{"tid":102983,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[成波之路] 叉燒醬烤雞翼 (影片+圖文食譜)","createTime":"2017-02-01T04:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T09:34:46.000Z","uid":35319,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc41ccbcef35eacfa4a4bf827580aff9b041c960","tid":102983,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"影片：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/A6WS5MP4AAA \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA6WS5MP4AAA%20&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8b015a33\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/A6WS5MP4AAA </a><br />\n叉燒醬除咗拎嚟整叉燒，仲可以用嚟整雞翼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好hea，不過真係簡單又好食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/6ina321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ina321.jpg&h=9ba92b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:\t<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=49c87fd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nInstagram:\t<a href=\"http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=73bd93ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nBlog:\t\t<a href=\"http://www.mywaystogetfat.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mywaystogetfat.com&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=49ed5811\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mywaystogetfat.com</a><br />\n<strong>Blog 可以睇返之前出過post既食譜</strong><br />\n有興趣請like/follow/睇睇啦，多謝你既留意同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>份量：15 隻雞翼<br />\n<ins>材料</ins></strong>\t<br />\n雞中翼\t15隻（500 克）<br />\n薑\t2片<br />\n叉燒醬\t4 湯匙<br />\n蜜糖\t2 湯匙<br />\n<br />\n1. 把雞中翼放到鍋中，注入常溫水至蓋面，加入薑片，以小火煮至接近滾起，夾起雞翼。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/8ijA56W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ijA56W.jpg&h=93de4254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 印乾雞中翼的水份。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/mQt0Q0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQt0Q0g.jpg&h=9952e4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 加入叉燒醬拌勻醃 2 小時或以上。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/49209D0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49209D0.jpg&h=ab3de7b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 預熱焗爐至200&deg;C。在烤盤上鋪上錫紙，再放上網架，在網架上掃油。放上雞中翼，正面向上，掃上醃料，放入焗爐中層焗 10 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/rg4f17B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frg4f17B.jpg&h=aa90fbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 取出把雞翼翻面，掃上醃料，再焗 10 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/6442fgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6442fgQ.jpg&h=550c9cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 取出，掃上蜜糖，多焗 1 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/81gu9q7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81gu9q7.jpg&h=b66fb1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 取出，把雞翼翻面，掃上蜜糖，最後多焗 1 分鐘即成。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/8xncpk9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xncpk9.jpg&h=1956e82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e216037a885328ef1e5a6750227a9c4c4e5f614f","tid":102983,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"影片：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/A6WS5MP4AAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA6WS5MP4AAA&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ceb8f16d\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/A6WS5MP4AAA</a>"},{"pid":"aa4bdae1696e8933085d759d964b429c62b96a47","tid":102983,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4de888c2012a1196518e285cb48e8848a416590","tid":102983,"uid":75422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:02:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454451b4d646980284ba8c001bf624ec7ec7e5b4","tid":102983,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b085b7eb757b1843603219f54f57255b93bc2a60","tid":102983,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4af6f64b5fa1fdd6e1799d3b9f541e24a099a4","tid":102983,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c177025ccb168fc96d7123c7afd768e2b1d7f1e","tid":102983,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"肥波 好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab38e4f06b44604a12402dcaeb706ea73e83dc5","tid":10298